---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Testimonials"
  description="Feedback from coaches, parents and families who have worked with Michael Mulhern Football Consultancy."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge">Testimonials</span>
      <h1>What clients say</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="testimonials">
        <article class="testimonial">
          <blockquote class="testimonial__quote">
            <p>
              I worked with Michael Mulhern while studying for my UEFA A Licence
              and also took part in a number of workshops. The support was
              thoughtful, challenging, and grounded in real coaching practice
              rather than theory alone.
            </p>
            <p>
              The mentoring process encouraged reflection, ownership, and a
              deeper understanding of learning environments in football. That
              approach had a significant impact on how I developed as a coach and
              stayed with me as I progressed into professional roles, including
              coaching at WSL level.
            </p>
            <p>
              I would strongly recommend this work to coaches and organisations
              who are serious about developing people, not just programmes.
            </p>
          </blockquote>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <span class="testimonial__name">Vicky Greenwell</span>
            <span class="testimonial__role">UEFA A Licence Coach, Former WSL Coach, University of Memphis alumni</span>
          </footer>
        </article>

        <article class="testimonial">
          <blockquote class="testimonial__quote">
            <p>
              We engaged with Michael to carry out a report for our son, hoping
              to gain a detailed understanding of his strengths and weaknesses so
              we could support his development. Michael observed our son on two
              separate occasions, as we wanted to see how he performed in
              different game settings. The way Michael handled the process was
              first class — he operated discreetly, ensuring our child had no
              idea he was being watched. We felt this approach gave us the most
              honest and accurate picture of our son as a player.
            </p>
            <p>
              The report Michael produced was incredible. The level of detail was
              outstanding, and the structure made it easy to follow and put into
              action. It was completely unbiased and honest, and what surprised
              us most was how clearly our son's character came through. After
              only two games, you would think Michael had known him far longer.
            </p>
            <p>
              The analysis of strengths and weaknesses was clear, constructive,
              and supported by a four-week development plan that we were able to
              implement immediately. We especially valued the separate parent and
              player sections. Our son could read about his strengths and areas
              for improvement in a way written specifically for him. The "bottle
              checklist" was a brilliant addition — simple, snappy, and something
              he now refers to during games, exactly as intended, helping him
              refocus before, during, and after matches.
            </p>
            <p>
              Another standout feature was the parents' checklist for what to say
              after a game. When emotions run high, it's the perfect reminder for
              any parent.
            </p>
            <p>
              We would absolutely recommend Michael to any parent with a player
              at any level who wants honest, professional guidance on how to help
              their child improve. He is a total professional who provides far
              more than just a report. The work he puts in beforehand to
              understand the player, the depth and clarity of the report itself,
              and the ongoing support he offers afterwards are truly outstanding.
            </p>
          </blockquote>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <span class="testimonial__name">Lisa Malloy</span>
            <span class="testimonial__role">Durham, UK</span>
          </footer>
        </article>

        <article class="testimonial">
          <blockquote class="testimonial__quote">
            <p>
              My son is a high level U13 goalkeeper. He kept asking me what areas
              he could improve on to try and get his chance to push into an
              academy. Being a parent with little knowledge in goalkeeping, I
              couldn't answer this. So after finding out about Michael Mulhern
              Football Consultancy, I got in touch with Michael who found out
              more about Kai. We all agreed that to get full knowledge of Kai's
              possible improvement areas it would be good to get a report on
              three matches rather than just one.
            </p>
            <p>
              After doing this and finding out the areas Kai needed to improve
              on, Michael wrote a full detailed report which also included a
              player and parent pack. After reading this and spending a classroom
              session with Michael, my son has massively improved on the areas
              that needed tweaked.
            </p>
            <p>
              We still have a way to go to get to academy level but Michael and
              my son meet up or chat weekly to improve on these areas. This has
              by far been the best decision in his football journey because we
              now know exactly what areas we need to work on.
            </p>
          </blockquote>
          <footer class="testimonial__author">
            <span class="testimonial__name">Steve Wood</span>
            <span class="testimonial__role">Berwick, UK</span>
          </footer>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header">
        <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
        <p>Get in touch to discuss how Michael can help.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta__action">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-off-white);
  }

  .page-header .badge {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .testimonials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .testimonial {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-grey-200);
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .testimonial:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .testimonial__quote {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-gold);
  }

  .testimonial__quote p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .testimonial__quote p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .testimonial__author {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.125rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-grey-200);
  }

  .testimonial__name {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  .testimonial__role {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-400);
  }

  .cta__action {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
